title: 208: Lions-Giants Recap, NFL Network’s Mike Mayock
itunes:title: 208: Lions-Giants Recap, NFL Network’s Mike Mayock
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the Detroit Lions' 24-10 win over the New York Giants on “Monday Night Football.” The guys also review the college football weekend and welcome in NFL Network’s Mike Mayock.
